These are Puzzles for 5x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, mirinda
The people have 2 different jobs:  social-worker, journalist
2 different pets are kept: frog, chinchilla
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: swimming, biathlon
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, taxi
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
2. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
3. the journalist is the owner of the frog##1
4. the social-worker is the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |
| Beverage    | fanta       | mirinda  |
| Job         | social-worker | journalist |
| Pet         | chinchilla        | frog     |
| Sport       | biathlon     | swimming  |
| Transport   | helicopter    | taxi     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk
The people have 2 different jobs:  teacher, bartender
2 different pets are kept: hamster, turtle
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: parkour, rowing
The people use 2 different means of transport: subway, jet-ski
1. the bartender is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the hamster is the person who's sport is rowing##1
4. the owner of the hamster is the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |       2       |
| Beverage    | 7up  | almond-milk        |
| Job         | bartender | teacher     |
| Pet         | turtle  | hamster        |
| Sport       | parkour  | rowing |
| Transport   | jet-ski      | subway        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-1-3::.
There 2 different types of food: plum, pear
The people have 2 different hobbies: writing, cooking
The people have 2 different jobs:  chef, dancer
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: techno, country
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, volleyball
1. the person eating pear is on the far left##1
2. the fan of country is on the right of the chef##1
3. the fan of techno is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |    2     |
| Food          | pear             | plum  |
| Hobby         | cooking         | writing  |
| Job           | chef | dancer  |
| Music-Genre   | techno         | country      |
| Sport         | volleyball      | sailing |

