.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-1-4::.
There 2 different types of food: pineapple, banana
The people have 2 different jobs:  dressmaker, lawyer
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: martial-arts, horror
There are 2 different nationalities: american, spanish
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, motorbike
1. the person eating banana is on the far right##1
2. the american is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
4. the lawyer is on the right of the dressmaker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Food          | pineapple    | banana     |
| Job           | dressmaker   | lawyer |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts   | horror     |
| Nationality   | american  | spanish    |
| Transport     | car | motorbike       |

