.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-1-20::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: rock-climbing, puzzles
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: adventure, action
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: indie, country
2 different pets are kept: snake, guinea-pig
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: surfing, skiing
1. the fan of country is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the person who's sport is surfing is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing     | puzzles |
| Movie-Genre   | action | adventure   |
| Music-Genre   | country      | indie |
| Pet           | guinea-pig         | snake     |
| Sport         | skiing  | surfing |

 